Félix León, J
Ochoa Urdangarain, O

metadata.dc:description: We report on a 52-year-old patient who presented with a right-sided tumor mass of the spermatic cord. We describe the operative and biopsy procedures and present our conclusions.
metadata.dc:title: Liposarcoma del cordón espermático. Presentación de un nuevo caso.
[Liposarcoma of the spermatic cord. Presentation of a new case].
